import React from 'react'
import { Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Aside from './Aside'
import Nav from './Nav'



function AdminPanel() {
    return (

        <>
            <Nav />
            <Aside />
            <Routes>
            <Route path="blogadd" element={<BlogAdd />} />
            </Routes>
        </>

    )
}

export default AdminPanel
